=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614607\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mlc1665702620662.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mlc1665702620662.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mlc1665702620662.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mlc1665702620662\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">ProcScript: Precompiler Directives and Uniface Constants\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Precompiler directives and Uniface constants enable you to produce generalized,\n      reusable ProcScript. They allow you to determine the exact composition of the ProcScript that\n      will be compiled.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__section_w2442ab1b5b1_w2443ab1b5_w2444ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__section_w2445ab1b5b3_w2446ab1b5_w2447ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d875494e57\">\n                 \n Precompiler Directives\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36359e1_d36360e1_d36361e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fmh1665702620740.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fmh1665702620740.html\" title=\"Define a comment in the generated code.\">#comment</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36362e1_d36363e1_d36364e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ots1665702620497.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ots1665702620497.html\" title=\"Define a constant name and value.\">#define</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qor1704696894707.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qor1704696894707.html\" title=\"Declares an alternative precompiler condition if none of the previous conditions have been met, and executes the containing ProcScripts and precompiler directives when the condition is met.\">#else</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ffk1704697377822.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ffk1704697377822.html\" title=\"Declares an alternative condition to that introduced by the preceding #if precompiler directive, and executes the containing ProcScripts and precompiler directives when the condition is met.\">#elseif</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36365e1_d36366e1_d36367e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rmq1665702620822.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmq1665702620822.html\" title=\"Declares the end scope of precompiler constants declared after the corresponding #startdefine.\">#enddefine</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nvb1704698671206.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nvb1704698671206.html\" title=\"Declares the end scope of the preceding corresponding #for precompiler directive.\">#endfor</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ele1704698708562.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ele1704698708562.html\" title=\"Declares the end scope of the preceding #if precompiler directive.\">#endif</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36368e1_d36369e1_d36370e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ysu1665702621045.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ysu1665702621045.html\" title=\"Insert a global ProcScript module as an entry module.\">#entry</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36371e1_d36372e1_d36373e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ycl1665702621117.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ycl1665702621117.html\" title=\"Produce a compiler error message.\">#error</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36374e1_d36375e1_d36376e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bus1665702621196.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bus1665702621196.html\" title=\"Generate blocks of repeated ProcScript.\">#for</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dya1676013505110.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dya1676013505110.html\" title=\"Insert a global ProcScript module.\">#function</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36377e1_d36378e1_d36379e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dyv1665702621269.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dyv1665702621269.html\" title=\"Conditionally generate ProcScript, depending on the results of the specified expressions.\">#if</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36380e1_d36381e1_d36382e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cew1665702621348.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cew1665702621348.html\" title=\"Test if a constant has been defined.\">#ifdefined</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36383e1_d36384e1_d36385e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"syc1665702621424.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/syc1665702621424.html\" title=\"Test if a constant has not been defined.\">#ifundefined</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36386e1_d36387e1_d36388e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yah1665702621497.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yah1665702621497.html\" title=\"Insert the contents of the specified IncludeScript in the location of the #include directive.\">#include</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36389e1_d36390e1_d36391e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pae1665702621575.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pae1665702621575.html\" title=\"Produce a compiler information message.\">#info</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36392e1_d36393e1_d36394e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"arp1665702621651.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/arp1665702621651.html\" title=\"Provides a specific instruction to the compiler.\">#pragma</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36395e1_d36396e1_d36397e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"unu1665702620895.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/unu1665702620895.html\" title=\"Declares the scope of precompiler constant declarations (#define's)\">#startdefine</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36398e1_d36399e1_d36400e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ktw1665702620584.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ktw1665702620584.html\" title=\"Undefine a constant for the scope of the constant declaration.\">#undefine</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36401e1_d36402e1_d36403e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aly1665702621728.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aly1665702621728.html\" title=\"Produce a compiler warning message.\">#warning</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__section_w2448ab1b5b5_w2449ab1b5_w2450ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d875494e274\">Uniface Constants\n         </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__p_d93014e1_d93015e1_d93016e1\">Uniface constants comprise a set of predefined constants that can be used in ProcScript to refer to objects and properties.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__note_w2451ab1b5b5b5_w2452ab1b5b5_w2453ab1b5_w2454ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> These constants should only be used in components, not in global ProcScript, because during compilation, global ProcScript does not have access to the information required to correctly resolve the constants.</div>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36404e1_d36405e1_d36406e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aau1665702621803.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aau1665702621803.html\" title=\"The &lt;$cmpStatemanagedBy&gt; constant determines how component state is managed for the server page or session service.\">&lt;$cmpStateManagedBy&gt;</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36407e1_d36408e1_d36409e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"omf1665702621883.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/omf1665702621883.html\" title=\"Component name\">&lt;$componentName&gt;</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36410e1_d36411e1_d36412e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nmb1665702621957.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nmb1665702621957.html\" title=\"Uniface component type\">&lt;$componentType&gt;</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36413e1_d36414e1_d36415e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ehh1665702622032.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ehh1665702622032.html\" title=\"Entity name\">&lt;$entName&gt;</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36416e1_d36417e1_d36418e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"azw1665702622107.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azw1665702622107.html\" title=\"Field name\">&lt;$fieldName&gt;</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36419e1_d36420e1_d36421e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"afq1665702622182.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/afq1665702622182.html\" title=\"The library in which a global object resides.\">&lt;$libraryName&gt;</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36422e1_d36423e1_d36424e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ooj1665702622258.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ooj1665702622258.html\" title=\"The value of the entity’s model name property.\">&lt;$modelName&gt;</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36425e1_d36426e1_d36427e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xhl1665702622337.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xhl1665702622337.html\" title=\"The entity's supertype.\">&lt;$tableName&gt;</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mlc1665702620662__li_d36428e1_d36429e1_d36430e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pop1665702622413.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pop1665702622413.html\" title=\"The trigger name abbreviation.\">&lt;$triggerAbbr&gt;</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xxw1665703019519.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Precompiler Directives: Descriptions</a><p>Precompiler directives are symbols used in ProcScript that are parsed and interpreted by the precompiler to insert or generate constants, IncludeScripts, and other code.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yyf1665703021884.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Predefined Constants: Descriptions</a><p>Uniface provides a set of predefined constants that can be used in ProcScript to refer to objects and properties, such as a field or entity.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614607\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614607\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ProcScript: Precompiler Directives and Uniface Constants Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 ProcScript: Precompiler Directives and Uniface Constants Precompiler directives and Uniface constants enable you to produce generalized, reusable ProcScript. They allow you to determine the exact composition of the ProcScript that will be compiled. Precompiler Directives #comment #define #else #elseif #enddefine #endfor #endif #entry #error #for #function #if #ifdefined #ifundefined #include #info #pragma #startdefine #undefine #warning Uniface Constants Uniface constants comprise a set of predefined constants that can be used in ProcScript to refer to objects and properties. Note: These constants should only be used in components, not in global ProcScript, because during compilation, global ProcScript does not have access to the information required to correctly resolve the constants. <$cmpStateManagedBy> <$componentName> <$componentType> <$entName> <$fieldName> <$libraryName> <$modelName> <$tableName> <$triggerAbbr> Related Links Precompiler Directives: Descriptions Precompiler directives are symbols used in ProcScript that are parsed and interpreted by the precompiler to insert or generate constants, IncludeScripts, and other code. Predefined Constants: Descriptions Uniface provides a set of predefined constants that can be used in ProcScript to refer to objects and properties, such as a field or entity. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}